flowchart TD
    Start([User Journey Start]) --> NewUser{New User?}

    NewUser -->|Yes| Register[Register Account]
    NewUser -->|No| Login[Login]

    Register --> VerifyEmail[Verify Email via OTP]
    VerifyEmail --> EmailVerified{Email Verified?}
    EmailVerified -->|No| ResendOTP[Resend OTP]
    ResendOTP --> VerifyEmail
    EmailVerified -->|Yes| CreateProfile[Create UserProfile]

    CreateProfile --> SetPreferences[Set Support Mode & Notification Style]
    SetPreferences --> CompleteRegistration[Registration Complete]

    Login --> AuthSuccess{Auth Success?}
    AuthSuccess -->|No| ShowError[Show Error Message]
    ShowError --> Login

    AuthSuccess -->|Yes| GetDashboard[Get Dashboard Data]

    CompleteRegistration --> GetDashboard

    GetDashboard --> ViewTasks[View Tasks]
    GetDashboard --> ViewGroups[View Groups]
    GetDashboard --> ViewNotifications[View Notifications]

    ViewTasks --> ManageTasks[Create/Update/Delete Tasks]
    ViewGroups --> ManageGroups[Join/Create Groups]
    ViewNotifications --> ManageNotifications[Mark Read/Unread]

    ManageTasks --> UpdateProfile[Update Profile]
    ManageGroups --> UpdateProfile
    ManageNotifications --> UpdateProfile

    UpdateProfile --> UpdateDevice[Update Device Info]
    UpdateDevice --> SyncCalendar[Sync Calendly Integration]
    SyncCalendar --> End([User Journey End])
